<%= render partial: 'shared/thape_nav', locals: { nav_background: 'white', show_debug: false } -%>

<div class="relative" x-data="{ activeSlide: 1, slides: [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6], show_left_btn: false, show_right_btn: false }"
  data-controller="carousel"
  data-carousel-turn-white="true"
  data-carousel-refresh-interval="5000">
  <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-h1.jpg', 'x-show': 'activeSlide === 1', class: "pt-12" -%>
  <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-h2.jpg', 'x-show': 'activeSlide === 2', class: "pt-12" -%>
  <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-h3.jpg', 'x-show': 'activeSlide === 3', class: "pt-12" -%>
  <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-h4.jpg', 'x-show': 'activeSlide === 4', class: "pt-12" -%>
  <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-h5.jpg', 'x-show': 'activeSlide === 5', class: "pt-12" -%>
  <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-h6.jpg', 'x-show': 'activeSlide === 6', class: "pt-12" -%>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full flex">
      <div class="w-1/4 flex justify-start items-center"
        x-on:mouseenter="show_left_btn = true"
        x-on:mouseleave="show_left_btn = false">
        <button
          x-on:click="activeSlide = activeSlide === 1 ? slides.length : activeSlide - 1">
          <svg class="ml-4 pt-1 w-6 h-8 fill-current" style="fill-rule:evenodd;clip-rule:evenodd;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-miterlimit:2;"
            x-bind:class="{ 'text-gray-300': show_left_btn, 'text-black6c-t70': !show_left_btn }">
              <g transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,-35,-81)">
                  <path d="M50.061,84.04L39.101,95L50.061,105.96C50.646,106.546 50.646,107.496 50.061,108.081C49.475,108.667 48.525,108.667 47.939,108.081L35.919,96.061C35.333,95.475 35.333,94.525 35.919,93.939L47.939,81.919C48.525,81.333 49.475,81.333 50.061,81.919C50.646,82.504 50.646,83.454 50.061,84.04Z" />
              </g>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="w-2/4" data-action="mouseenter->carousel#stop_rotate mouseleave->carousel#start_rotate"></div>
      <div class="w-1/4 flex justify-end items-center"
        x-on:mouseenter="show_right_btn = true"
        x-on:mouseleave="show_right_btn = false">
        <button
          data-target="carousel.nextSlide"\
          x-on:click="activeSlide = activeSlide === slides.length ? 1 : activeSlide + 1">
          <svg class="mr-4 pt-1 w-6 h-8 fill-current" style="fill-rule:evenodd;clip-rule:evenodd;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-miterlimit:2;"
            x-bind:class="{ 'text-gray-300': show_right_btn, 'text-black6c-t70': !show_right_btn }">
              <g transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,-125,-81)">
                <path d="M139.582,96.544L127.587,108.551C127.002,109.136 126.054,109.136 125.47,108.551C124.885,107.966 124.885,107.017 125.47,106.432L136.407,95.484L125.47,84.537C124.885,83.952 124.885,83.003 125.47,82.418C126.054,81.833 127.002,81.833 127.587,82.418L139.582,94.425C140.167,95.01 140.167,95.959 139.582,96.544Z" />
              </g>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 bg-white opacity-75">
    <div class="sm:flex px-10 sm:px-20 md:px-32 lg:px-40 xl:px-48 xxl:px-56 xxxl:px-64">
      <dt class="w-1/3 font-medium text-black6c pt-2">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold whitespace-no-wrap">创意与技术完美融合</h1>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium whitespace-no-wrap">ENGINEERING POWERED. </h2>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium whitespace-no-wrap">DESIGN ACHIEVED.</h2>
      </dt>
      <dd class="w-2/3 text-sm font-light text-black6c text-justify p-3">
        <p>上海天华建筑设计有限公司（以下简称天华）创立于1997年，由上海天祥实业有限公司控股，是中国首批甲级民营建筑设计公司之一，专注于提供城市建设领域的专业服务，为政府和企业客户等提供全面而专业的综合解决方案与全程卓越客户体验。 </p>
        <p>天华，服务范围涵盖城市规划、建筑设计、室内设计、景观设计、技术咨询到建筑审图、可视化、BIM正向设计等全方位服务。科学统筹“咨询、设计、技术、管理”互联的高效服务模式，因地制宜地为不同城市建设项目提供具有创新性和经济性的解决方案。目前，天华35个子公司遍布于全国22个城市，汇聚了5600多位优秀人才。我们与客户，上下游合作伙伴一起，助力城市持续发展。 </p>
        <p>天华以客户需求和前沿发展理念及技术为驱动力，将富有特色的方案与强大的技术相结合，致力于对设计高品质完美实现的追求，打造“创意与技术完美融合”的品牌理念。  </p>
      </dd>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-1 sm:gap-2 my-2">
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-black" x-data="{ show_g1: false }" x-on:mouseenter="show_g1 = true" x-on:mouseleave="show_g1 = false">
    <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-g1.jpg', class: 'grid-mask-image hover:scale-105' -%>
    <div class="absolute text-white left-6 bottom-4" x-show="!show_g1">
      <p class="text-xl text-left pb-1 font-medium">研究</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-left leading-snug">RESEARCH</p>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black6c-t70 text-white flex content-center justify-left" x-show="show_g1"
      x-transition:enter="transition ease-linear duration-200"
      x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 transform -translate-x-1/2"
      x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 transform translate-x-0"
      x-transition:leave="transition ease-in duration-200"
      x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100 transform translate-x-0"
      x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0 transform -translate-x-1/2">
      <div class="w-7/12 xxl:w-2/3 mt-32 ml-10">
        <h1 class="text-2xl xl:text-3xl text-left pb-1 font-semibold">研究</h1>
        <h2 class="text-xl xl:text-2xl text-left leading-snug">RESEARCH</h2>
        <h3 class="mt-8 xl:mt-10 xxl:mt-12 text-base xl:text-lg xxl:text-xl font-bold text-left">技术赋能设计——基于创新的研究</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs xl:text-sm xxl:text-base text-justify">基于社会责任感和对设计品质的执着追求，天华近年相继前瞻性地成立了八大研究中心，积极探索和研发相关课题，发挥大型综合设计企业的优势，与境内外高校联合展开多项探索性研究，策略和实践双轮驱动，在上述领域积累了丰富的策略、技术和实践成果，组建了天华的专家团队。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-black">
    <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-g2.jpg', class: 'grid-mask-image hover:scale-105' -%>
    <div class="absolute text-white left-6 bottom-4">
      <p class="text-xl text-left pb-1 font-medium">THDL</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-left leading-snug">Tianhua Design Lab</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-black">
    <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-g3.jpg', class: 'grid-mask-image hover:scale-105' -%>
    <div class="absolute text-white left-6 bottom-4">
      <p class="text-xl text-left pb-1 font-medium">T+ </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-left leading-snug">T Plus</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-black">
    <a href="<%= work_path(id: 1) -%>" class="cursor-pointer">
      <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/about-g4.jpg', class: 'grid-mask-image hover:scale-105' -%>
      <div class="absolute text-white left-6 bottom-4">
        <p class="text-xl text-left pb-1 font-medium">黑标住宅</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-left leading-snug">PERFECTION PURSUER</p>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<%= render partial: 'shared/footer' %>
